  76:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_eth.c ****           (##) HAL_ETH_GetDMAConfig(): Get DMA actual configuration into ETH_DMAConfigTypeDef
  77:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_eth.c ****           (##) HAL_ETH_SetDMAConfig(): Set DMA configuration based on ETH_DMAConfigTypeDef
  78:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_eth.c **** 
